Subject: drm/ttm: Don't unreserve swapped BOs that were previously reserved
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: ad76c65ec39f20139885ecd4e5830f2c2a643dcb
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

If ttm_bo_swapout doesn't own the lock, don't release it. Someone
else probably depends on it still being locked.

